108
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:27,860
Then I'll stay with you for a while.

109
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:28,660
Do you mind?

110
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:29,300
Of course not.

111
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:31,380
Why don't you come in with me
for a cup of tea?

112
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,620
You are sensible.

113
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,860
I'm thirsty.

114
00:05:37,020 --> 00:05:38,380
Come one.

115
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:39,380
Go.

116
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:47,140
Look at your face,

117
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:49,100
