118
00:05:50,660 --> 00:05:52,100
So I'm not a monkey butt.

119
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:52,820
You.

120
00:05:54,020 --> 00:05:54,780
You're laughing.

121
00:05:57,660 --> 00:05:58,980
Look at what you've done.

122
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:02,060
Split the door with one hand.

123
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:05,020
Why don't you split the door
into two halves?

124
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:06,700
Don't you know
Your Highness likes symmetry?

125
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,900
Eunuch Song, is that really the point?

126
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:11,740
Yes.

127
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:13,860
No.

128
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:16,660
Your Highness, please get to the point.

129
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:22,340
Now that you have entered the palace,

130
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:25,420
