147
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:41,540
It's just ordinary pastry.

148
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:43,900
Don't you usually have pastries at home?

149
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,740
Pastries.

150
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:47,700
Infrequently bought.

151
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:59,380
Who is so ignorant?

152
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,260
Run.

153
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:07,300
My dad and the others

154
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:09,180
like to eat roast chicken feet

155
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,420
and haggis.

156
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:13,620
And stinky tofu from Grandma Xing's
on Xuanwu Street.

157
00:08:13,820 --> 00:08:15,820
Slightly smelly, medium, and extra.

158
00:08:15,820 --> 00:08:17,540
Be sure to eat the extra kind.

159
00:08:18,620 --> 00:08:20,380
Grand Chancellor

160
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:21,900
