161
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,180
and unrestrained privately.

162
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:24,460
What a surprise.

163
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:29,220
Have some tea.

164
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:44,700
So what exactly is this place?

165
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,780
This is Tianji Mansion.

166
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:49,900
Does Tianji
means the secreat cannot be disclosed?

167
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:50,940
Exactly.

168
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:54,740
Isn't this a fortune-telling stand

169
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:55,860
