191
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,420
If he can't tell something good,

192
00:09:56,420 --> 00:09:58,220
I can go back and scare that girl.

193
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,300
See something?

194
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:14,300
You are a girl with great ideas.

195
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:16,420
Discursive nature.

196
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:18,300
Hate to follow the rules.

197
00:10:18,820 --> 00:10:21,100
Your life is not smooth.

198
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:24,340
And you seem to have encountered

199
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:26,020
