200
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,340
Can he do the divination or not?

201
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:33,100
Obviously it is Mei Daidai's hand.

202
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,780
Why does it sound like it's me?

203
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:37,860
Stop, I don't want to continue.

204
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:38,900
Well.

205
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,260
Why don't you take me out for a walk?

206
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:42,740
Okay.

207
00:10:42,900 --> 00:10:44,980
What hobbies do you have?

208
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:47,260
I'm interested in everything.

209
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:49,260
Come on.

210
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:51,260
Come with me.

211
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:53,820
[Xingqing Hall]

212
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,180
Your Highness.

213
00:10:55,820 --> 00:10:57,980
